{"tid":1759782,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"好多戰線要打，好多任務要打","createTime":"2019-11-28T00:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T12:05:43.000Z","uid":76310,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5bcb1c141f48be36289ce0cfe1820cd5eb2190de","tid":1759782,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:04:45.000Z","msg":"點解成班人好似無氣既氣球咁<br />\n大把支線任務<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動類：<br />\n遊行/集會/和你shop/和你唱/開花<br />\n<br />\n國際線：<br />\n揭露警暴/選舉不公/一国二制是假象/司法不公/香港比中国直接操控/抵制<br />\n<br />\n議會線：<br />\n功能組別/立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n經濟線：<br />\n打擊藍店/mpf/黃色經濟圈/捐錢支持義士<br />\n<br />\n文宣線：<br />\n連儂牆/打擊cctvb/打擊紅謀/完全紀錄警暴<br />\n<br />\n我應該數漏左好多<br />\n但基本數一數已經咁多<br />\n每樣野都大把野做"},{"pid":"ec0983c56ace22887a1e5cf2421a448b5bfba930","tid":1759782,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:19:52.000Z","msg":"特朗普簽左法案啦！快啲多謝幫過手的議員啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1759783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1759783</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dfb965187de755e32a0175415776e8062b77012f","tid":1759782,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"大家應該好唔得閒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f702fd5cd210c707a00effba9d49e758884bf0","tid":1759782,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1ea263cb59e8cef1706de4ecdef9b43fdb1cb5","tid":1759782,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:33:59.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155fef7f8252c05c5f70173f7401c38242d69f59","tid":1759782,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28